  "docsGettingStartedTitle": "Welcome to Aura In",
  "docsGettingStartedSubtitle": "The marketplace platform for service-based businesses",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsTitle": "What is Aura In?",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsSubtitle": "Understand the platform",
  "docsGettingStartedWelcomeIntroContent": "Aura In is a mobile marketplace connecting service professionals with customers. Whether you offer haircuts, massages, freelance services, or sell products, this platform helps you grow your business.",
  "docsGettingStartedWhoUsesTitle": "Who Uses Aura In?",
  "docsGettingStartedWhoUsesContent": "Two types of users power the platform:",
  "docsGettingStartedWhoUsesProviders": "Service Providers - Salons, spas, barbers, freelancers who offer services",
  "docsGettingStartedWhoUsesCustomers": "Customers - People searching for and booking services in their area",
  "docsGettingStartedWhoUsesSellers": "Product Sellers - Shops selling retail products or handmade items",
  "docsGettingStartedHowItWorksTitle": "How It Works",
  "docsGettingStartedHowItWorksContent": "Service providers create a profile, list their services with pricing, and accept bookings from customers. Customers search by location, browse services, and book appointments. Everything is managed through the app.",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeWaysTitle": "Three Ways to Use Aura In",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeWaysSubtitle": "Choose your role",
  "docsGettingStartedOption1Title": "Option 1: Browse & Book Services (Customer)",
  "docsGettingStartedOption1Content": "Search for salons, massage therapists, barbers, or freelancers near you. View their services, pricing, and availability. Book appointments directly through the app and pay securely.",
  "docsGettingStartedGuestBookingTitle": "Guest Booking (No App Download Needed)",
  "docsGettingStartedGuestBookingContent": "Don't want to download the app? Service providers can share a booking link - you can book and pay directly through that link without creating an account. Your booking details and receipt will be sent to your WhatsApp.",
  "docsGettingStartedOption2Title": "Option 2: Offer Services (Shop Owner or Freelancer)",
  "docsGettingStartedOption2Content": "Create a shop or freelancer profile, list your services with pricing and duration, set your working hours, and manage bookings. Get paid for every service booked.",
  "docsGettingStartedOption3Title": "Option 3: Sell Products (Product Seller)",
  "docsGettingStartedOption3Content": "If you make handmade items or retail products, you can list them for sale. Customers browse and purchase directly from your shop.",
  "docsGettingStartedBookingPaymentTitle": "Booking & Payment System",
  "docsGettingStartedBookingPaymentSubtitle": "How service booking and payment work",
  "docsGettingStartedBookingOverviewContent": "Customers book appointments with service providers. Payments are handled securely through the app using Paystack (Africa) or Stripe (Global).",
  "docsGettingStartedDepositPaymentTitle": "Deposit Payment (30%)",
  "docsGettingStartedDepositPaymentContent": "When booking a service, customers pay 30% upfront as a deposit to secure the time slot. This confirms the booking is real and reserved.",
  "docsGettingStartedPlatformFeeTitle": "Platform Fee",
  "docsGettingStartedPlatformFeeContent": "A small platform fee (2%) is added to help us maintain the platform and provide support. This is calculated on the total booking amount.",
  "docsGettingStartedRemainingPaymentTitle": "Remaining Payment (70%)",
  "docsGettingStartedRemainingPaymentContent": "The remaining 70% can be paid either: (1) in cash when the service is completed, or (2) online through the app before the appointment.",
  "docsGettingStartedGuestBookingPaymentTitle": "Guest Booking Payment",
  "docsGettingStartedGuestBookingPaymentContent": "No app download needed! Customers receive a booking link from the service provider. They pay 30% to secure the slot, and their receipt is sent to WhatsApp.",
  "docsGettingStartedProductOrderingTitle": "Product Ordering & Delivery",
  "docsGettingStartedProductOrderingSubtitle": "How product sales work",
  "docsGettingStartedProductOverviewContent": "Customers browse products, add items to cart, and checkout. Products are delivered to the customer's location.",
  "docsGettingStartedCODPaymentTitle": "Cash on Delivery (COD)",
  "docsGettingStartedCODPaymentContent": "For product orders, payment is handled as Cash on Delivery. Customers pay the seller when they receive the items - no upfront payment needed.",
  "docsGettingStartedShareYourProfileTitle": "Share Your Profile",
  "docsGettingStartedShareYourProfileSubtitle": "Make it easy for customers to find you",
  "docsGettingStartedShareLinkContent": "As a service provider, you get a unique booking link. Share it on WhatsApp, social media, or email. Customers can book services without downloading the app.",
  "docsGettingStartedCustomURLTitle": "Custom URL (Optional)",
  "docsGettingStartedCustomURLContent": "You can customize your booking link slug (e.g., aura.in/glamour-salon instead of aura.in/abc123). Makes it easier to share and remember.",
  "docsGettingStartedGetHelpTitle": "Get Help",
  "docsGettingStartedGetHelpSubtitle": "Where to find answers",
  "docsGettingStartedHelpDocumentationContent": "This app has comprehensive documentation for every feature. When you need help, check the relevant guide - there's one for your role and the feature you're using.",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ1Question": "What is Aura In?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ1Answer": "Aura In is a mobile marketplace for service-based businesses. Customers find and book services (haircuts, massages, etc.), service providers manage bookings and revenue, and product sellers list items for sale.",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ2Question": "Do I need to pay to use the app?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ2Answer": "The app is free to download and use. Service providers only pay a small commission when customers pay for services. Payment processors (Paystack/Stripe) take a fee.",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ3Question": "What is the difference between Shop Owner and Freelancer?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ3Answer": "Shop owners have a fixed location with a team of workers. Freelancers work independently and can travel to clients. Choose based on your business model.",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ4Question": "How do I get paid?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ4Answer": "When customers pay for services, money goes to your wallet. You can withdraw to your bank account using Paystack (Africa) or Stripe (Global).",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ5Question": "Is my payment information secure?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ5Answer": "Yes. Aura In uses Paystack and Stripe, industry-leading payment processors with bank-level security. We never see your payment details.",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ6Question": "How do I know if service providers near me are trustworthy?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ6Answer": "Every service provider has ratings and reviews from customers who have booked with them. Read reviews before booking. High ratings mean consistent, quality service.",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ7Question": "Can I book without downloading the app?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ7Answer": "Yes! Service providers share a unique booking link. You can book directly through that link without downloading the app. Your receipt will be sent to WhatsApp.",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ8Question": "How much do I pay upfront for bookings?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ8Answer": "You pay 30% of the service total upfront to secure the booking slot (plus a 2% platform fee). The remaining 70% can be paid in cash or online before/at the service.",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ9Question": "How do I pay for products?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ9Answer": "Products use Cash on Delivery (COD). You pay the seller when you receive the items. This lets you check quality before paying and works well for local deliveries.",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ10Question": "Why the 2% platform fee?",
  "docsGettingStartedFAQ10Answer": "The platform fee helps us maintain Aura In, provide payment processing, customer support, and continuously improve features for both customers and service providers.",
  "docsBookingStartedTitle": "Getting Started with Bookings",
  "docsBookingStartedSubtitle": "A simple guide to understanding how bookings work",
  "docsBookingIntroTitle": "Welcome to the Booking System",
  "docsBookingIntroSubtitle": "Everything you need to know about booking services, whether you're a client or a shop owner.",
  "docsBookingWhatIsTitle": "What is the Booking System?",
  "docsBookingWhatIsContent": "The booking system is your gateway to scheduling services at your favorite shops. Whether you need a haircut, beard trim, braiding, or any other service, the system makes it easy to book appointments at your convenience.",
  "docsBookingWhoIsForTitle": "Who is this guide for?",
  "docsBookingWhoIsForContent": "This guide is designed for two types of users:",
  "docsBookingWhoIsForClients": "Clients: People who want to book services at shops",
  "docsBookingWhoIsForGuests": "Guest Bookers: People who want to book via a link without creating an account",
  "docsBookingWhoIsForOwners": "Shop Owners: People who manage shops, services, and workers",
  "docsBookingGuestIntroTitle": "New: Book Without Downloading the App",
  "docsBookingGuestIntroContent": "No account? No problem! If a shop owner shares a booking link with you, you can book directly without downloading the app. Your receipt is sent to WhatsApp.",
  "docsBookingWelcomeTip": "No technical knowledge needed! This guide uses simple language and real examples to help you understand everything.",
  "docsBookingAccountTitle": "Creating Your Account (Or Booking as Guest)",
  "docsBookingAccountSubtitle": "Get started in minutes - with or without an account",
  "docsBookingTwoWaysTitle": "Two Ways to Book",
  "docsBookingTwoWaysContent": "You can book in two ways:",
  "docsBookingTwoWaysAccount": "With Account: Download app, create account, book anytime",
  "docsBookingTwoWaysGuest": "As Guest: Use booking link, no app needed, receipt via WhatsApp",
  "docsBookingAccountStepsTitle": "How to Create an Account",
  "docsBookingAccountStepsContent": "Follow these simple steps to create your account:",
  "docsBookingAccountTypesTitle": "Account Types",
  "docsBookingAccountTypesContent": "There are two types of accounts:",
  "docsBookingAccountTypesClient": "Client Account: For booking services at shops",
  "docsBookingAccountTypesShop": "Shop Owner Account: For managing your own shop (requires approval)",
  "docsBookingGuestOptionTitle": "Booking as a Guest (No Account)",
  "docsBookingGuestOptionContent": "If someone shares a booking link with you, you can book directly without creating an account. Just click the link and follow the steps. Your receipt is sent to your WhatsApp.",
  "docsBookingVerificationNote": "You can browse and book without an account using a booking link. Creating an account gives you access to booking history, saved payments, and loyalty rewards.",
  "docsBookingFirstBookingTitle": "Your First Booking",
  "docsBookingFirstBookingSubtitle": "A quick walkthrough",
  "docsBookingPaymentTitle": "How Payment Works",
  "docsBookingPaymentContent": "When you book a service, here's how payment works:",
  "docsBookingPaymentDeposit": "30% Deposit Required: To secure your booking, you pay 30% of the total service cost upfront",
  "docsBookingPaymentNonRefundable": "Non-Refundable: This deposit is non-refundable if you cancel or don't show up",
  "docsBookingPaymentRemaining": "Remaining Balance: The remaining 70% is paid after your service is completed",
  "docsBookingPaymentSecure": "Secure Payment: All payments are processed securely through our payment partners",
  "docsBookingDepositNote": "The 30% deposit protects both you and the shop. It ensures your slot is reserved exclusively for you, and compensates the worker if you cancel last minute.",
  "docsBookingBookingTip": "Pro tip: Book at least 24 hours in advance for the best selection of time slots, especially for popular services.",
  "docsBookingAfterTitle": "After You Book",
  "docsBookingAfterSubtitle": "What happens next",
  "docsBookingWhatsNextTitle": "Your Booking is Confirmed!",
  "docsBookingWhatsNextContent": "Here's what you can do after booking:",
  "docsBookingRemindersTitle": "Booking Reminders",
  "docsBookingRemindersContent": "You'll receive reminders at:",
  "docsBookingAfterServiceTitle": "After Your Service",
  "docsBookingAfterServiceContent": "Once your service is complete:",
  "docsPaymentTitle": "Payment & Fees Explained",
  "docsPaymentSubtitle": "How 30% deposits, platform fees, and guest bookings work",
  "docsPaymentOverviewTitle": "How Payment Works",
  "docsPaymentOverviewSubtitle": "Simple, transparent, secure",
  "docsPaymentSummaryTitle": "Payment at a Glance",
  "docsPaymentSummaryContent": "Our payment system is designed to be fair for both clients and shop owners. Here's the simple breakdown:",
  "docsPaymentDeposit30": "30% Deposit: Paid at booking to secure your appointment",
  "docsPaymentPlatformFee": "Platform Fee: Small fixed fee (e.g., GHS 2) charged by the app",
  "docsPaymentRemaining70": "Remaining 70%: Paid after your service is complete",
  "docsPaymentTwoWays": "Two Ways to Pay Remaining: Cash or via app",
  "docsPaymentQuickExampleTitle": "Quick Example",
  "docsPaymentQuickExampleContent": "Service cost: GHS 100\nAt booking: Pay GHS 30 (deposit) + GHS 2 (fee) = GHS 32\nAfter service: Pay GHS 70 (cash or app)\nTotal to shop: GHS 100\nPlatform fee: GHS 2",
  "docsPaymentImportantNote": "The platform fee is charged by the app, not the shop. It helps us maintain the platform and provide you with a great booking experience.",
  "docsPaymentGuestBookingTitle": "Guest Booking (No App Download)",
  "docsPaymentGuestBookingContent": "Don't have the app? No problem! You can still book through your provider's booking link without creating an account. You pay the same 30% deposit + platform fee, and your receipt is sent to WhatsApp.",
  "docsDepositTitle": "The 30% Deposit",
  "docsDepositSubtitle": "Why it's needed and how it works",
  "docsDepositWhyTitle": "Why Do We Require a Deposit?",
  "docsDepositWhyContent": "The 30% deposit protects both you and the shop:",
  "docsDepositProtectsYou": "For you: Your slot is guaranteed – no one else can book it",
  "docsDepositProtectsShop": "For the shop: Workers are compensated if you cancel last minute",
  "docsDepositProtectsEveryone": "For everyone: Reduces no-shows, keeping prices fair",
  "docsDepositCalcTitle": "How the Deposit is Calculated",
  "docsDepositCalcContent": "The deposit is always 30% of the total service cost. This includes:",
  "docsDepositCalcSingle": "Single service: 30% of that service price",
  "docsDepositCalcMultiple": "Multiple services: 30% of all services combined",
  "docsDepositCalcGroup": "Group bookings: 30% of total for all people",
